---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="关于我们"
  description="馋猫有谱是一个专业的美食食谱网站，致力于提供详细的食谱步骤、食材百科、烹饪秘方和美食知识库，让每一个人都能做出靠谱的美味。"
  keywords="关于馋猫有谱,美食网站,食谱网站介绍"
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container about-container">
      <!-- 标题区 -->
      <div class="about-header">
        <div class="about-logo">
          <img src="/images/logo.png?v=3" alt="馋猫有谱" />
        </div>
        <h1 class="about-title">
          <span class="char-highlight">馋</span>得明白，做得靠<span class="char-highlight">谱</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="about-subtitle">他做的好，因为有谱，只要靠谱，你也可以</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 我们是谁 -->
      <div class="about-section">
        <h2 class="about-section-title">🍜 我们是谁</h2>
        <div class="about-content">
          <p>馋猫有谱是一个专注于中餐美食的内容平台。我们相信，<strong>好味道是可以复制的</strong>——只要有靠谱的配方、详细的步骤和对食材的理解，每个人都能做出好吃的菜。</p>
          <p>我们不追求网红爆款，也不做花里胡哨的摆盘。我们只想把<strong>真正好吃、家常、可落地</strong>的菜谱和美食知识，认认真真地整理出来，分享给每一个爱吃、爱做饭的人。</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 内容特色 -->
      <div class="about-section">
        <h2 class="about-section-title">✨ 内容特色</h2>
        <div class="feature-grid">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">📖</div>
            <h3>详细步骤</h3>
            <p>每道菜都有完整的步骤说明，从食材处理到火候把控，新手也能一步步跟着做。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">🥬</div>
            <h3>食材百科</h3>
            <p>系统介绍常见食材的特点、搭配、禁忌和处理方法，让你不仅会做，更懂食材。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">🗝️</div>
            <h3>独家秘方</h3>
            <p>收集整理各类调味秘方、酱汁配比和烹饪技巧，掌握核心原理，举一反三。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">🧠</div>
            <h3>美食知识库</h3>
            <p>从烹饪原理到饮食文化，从营养搭配到厨具选择，系统学习美食相关知识。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 数据统计 -->
      <div class="about-section stats-section">
        <div class="stat-item">
          <div class="stat-number">84</div>
          <div class="stat-label">精选食谱</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <div class="stat-number">156</div>
          <div class="stat-label">食材词条</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <div class="stat-number">38</div>
          <div class="stat-label">独家秘方</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <div class="stat-number">49</div>
          <div class="stat-label">知识文章</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 联系我们 -->
      <div class="about-section">
        <h2 class="about-section-title">📮 联系我们</h2>
        <div class="about-content">
          <p>如果你有任何问题、建议，或者想分享你的美食故事，欢迎通过以下方式找到我们：</p>
          <ul class="contact-list">
            <li>
              <span class="contact-icon">📧</span>
              <span>邮箱：</span>
              <a href="mailto:contact@chanmaoyoupu.com">contact@chanmaoyoupu.com</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="contact-icon">💬</span>
              <span>微信公众号：</span>
              <strong>馋猫有谱</strong>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p class="contact-tip">关注公众号，每天收到一道精选食谱推送 🍳</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 快速导航 -->
      <div class="about-section cta-section">
        <h2 class="about-section-title">🚀 开始探索</h2>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/recipes" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">浏览食谱</a>
          <a href="/ingredients" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg">食材百科</a>
          <a href="/secrets" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg">独家秘方</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-container {
    max-width: 820px;
  }

  .about-header {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px 0 60px;
  }

  .about-logo {
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .about-logo img {
    width: 100px;
    height: 100px;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 4px 16px rgba(255, 140, 66, 0.2));
  }

  .about-title {
    font-size: 2.4rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-title);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .char-highlight {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .about-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .about-section {
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .about-section-title {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-title);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    padding-bottom: 10px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-accent-light);
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .about-content p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .about-content p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  .about-content strong {
    color: var(--color-title);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* 特色网格 */
  .feature-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .feature-card {
    padding: 24px;
    background: var(--color-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    transition: all 0.25s;
  }
  .feature-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.08);
  }
  .feature-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .feature-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-title);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .feature-card p {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* 数据统计 */
  .stats-section {
    padding: 32px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFF5F0 0%, #FFFFFF 100%);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    border: 1px solid #FFE0CC;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-around;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .stat-number {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  /* 联系方式 */
  .contact-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 16px 0;
  }
  .contact-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 8px 0;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  .contact-icon {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }
  .contact-list a {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .contact-list a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  .contact-tip {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-top: 8px !important;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* CTA */
  .cta-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding-top: 20px;
  }
  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .btn-lg {
    padding: 12px 28px;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }
  .btn-outline {
    background: transparent;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--color-border);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  .btn-outline:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-header {
      padding: 20px 0 40px;
    }
    .about-title {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
    }
    .feature-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .stats-section {
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 20px;
      padding: 24px 16px;
    }
    .stat-item {
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 80px;
    }
    .stat-number {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
    }
    .cta-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .btn-lg {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
